56110,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:55:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"caa8199cf458c97d031a3096301ef94817d0e8ab","tid":56110,"uid":5399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T04:08:46.000Z","msg":"快樂 是陽光普照的精神"},{"pid":"7ab348687762750f19bdd0c4d3c71b4ef06a2624","tid":56110,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T04:25:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做你鐘意， 有成功感， 可以忘我投入嘅野</blockquote><br />\n呢三樣野。好難下&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n我都唔知鐘意咩<br />\n<br />\n所以無試過成功感，同埋投入唔到"},{"pid":"d4bfed60dbe6802c8c6a97a117d94b27502837ea","tid":56110,"uid":5479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T04:30:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做你鐘意， 有成功感， 可以忘我投入嘅野</blockquote><br />\n呢三樣野。好難下&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n我都唔知鐘意咩<br />\n<br />\n所以無試過成功感，同埋投入唔到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你冇野好做嫁喇喎"},{"pid":"751545391b43e891309044fe04c0934531ad8705","tid":56110,"uid":35816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T04:32:30.000Z","msg":"smoke weed"},{"pid":"a320f4d50732ed72a6539aeb374eb1a632b37ee3","tid":56110,"uid":342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T04:39:09.000Z","msg":"耶撚嘅感恩其實係知足常樂嘅極端版<br />\n<br />\n你唔使見到條草都要感恩<br />\n<br />\n但至少追到架巴士會覺得好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n收工食啲零食會覺得好食 滿足<br />\nkeep住正面啲<br />\n<br />\n仲有就係微笑 平時笑唔笑得出都試下keep住揚起嘴角 放鬆眼部周圍嘅肌肉 慢慢個人會從容啲 睇野都會正面啲"},{"pid":"be382db529e612b97b1f0cdda8b80ce0d3c46946","tid":56110,"uid":24063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T04:43:51.000Z","msg":"打丁"},{"pid":"9bf4a8a486fed5e61a66146abdf7fed0a8560796","tid":56110,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T04:58:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>&lt;blockquote&gt;做你鐘意， 有成功感， 可以忘我投入嘅野</blockquote><br />\n呢三樣野。好難下&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n我都唔知鐘意咩<br />\n<br />\n所以無試過成功感，同埋投入唔到&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n<br />\n咁你冇野好做嫁喇喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以我先要問je<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我試過唔同生活模式。但都係唔快樂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n試過好chur咁好忙咁，又試過hea下hea下咁，又試過百無聊賴咁&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都係唔開心"},{"pid":"1c8ef62fd86e1c4224dae1ecab3612a7f15f14d2","tid":56110,"uid":35857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:01:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>快樂 是陽光普照的精神</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4b04c68dc933f337ebc2f5d533a94dcbcc7ac51","tid":56110,"uid":8199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:06:48.000Z","msg":"錢"},{"pid":"e70afd6f21bf441bc0c0ac3ffa6086a136c83124","tid":56110,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:15:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但至少追到架巴士會覺得好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n收工食啲零食會覺得好食 滿足<br />\nkeep住正面啲<br />\n<br />\n仲有就係微笑 平時笑唔笑得出都試下keep住揚起嘴角 放鬆眼部周圍嘅肌肉 慢慢個人會從容啲 睇野都會正面啲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都試緊<br />\n<br />\n但係生活中挫折既數目比你上面所講既「小確幸」為多。<br />\n<br />\n所以滿足好少，唔夠維持一整日。"},{"pid":"b93311cf5fb91757b8a64ee1b1d3e03bb89c3110","tid":56110,"uid":49210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:16:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>知足常樂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如何知足</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n 對你而家擁有嘅嘢要有正面嘅 評價同珍惜， 唔好成日同啲人比較 。 對有難度要得到嘅嘢 要明白慢慢積累 係必須嘅， 千祈唔好以為即刻可以得到， 識得咩時候要放棄。"},{"pid":"5216e6cb610a4d77ff8ac0918485abf256fc3d31","tid":56110,"uid":64491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:19:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9707557356a98b80ffd10ea437223776a15a68f7","tid":56110,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:30:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>&lt;blockquote&gt;知足常樂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如何知足&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n<br />\n 對你而家擁有嘅嘢要有正面嘅 評價同珍惜， 唔好成日同啲人比較 。 對有難度要得到嘅嘢 要明白慢慢積累 係必須嘅， 千祈唔好以為即刻可以得到， 識得咩時候要放棄。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我所失的&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;竟已&hellip;&hellip;是我的所有"},{"pid":"b3aa6e810e56190f08d1232e593200098f8f6e99","tid":56110,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:38:09.000Z","msg":"人就係透過長時間嘅痛苦去完成某目標而得到短時間嘅快樂 但我唔認為足夠對沖痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f8efd91dcb2eaaf41347e67bb67ac2f353622eb","tid":56110,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:47:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人就係透過長時間嘅痛苦去完成某目標而得到短時間嘅快樂 但我唔認為足夠對沖痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唉"},{"pid":"94c045f1e5aee5bf53350530d330ecc9b5708024","tid":56110,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:56:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人就係透過長時間嘅痛苦去完成某目標而得到短時間嘅快樂 但我唔認為足夠對沖痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而且目標失敗的話 只會陷入更痛苦嘅環境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}